data.description: Charming 3 Bed, 1.5 Bath Home in Park Forest. Your Perfect Oasis! This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5 bathroom residence is a delightful combination of classic design and modern amenities, offering you a comfortable and inviting living space. Spacious living room with abundant natural light, perfect for family gatherings. Well-appointed kitchen with ample cabinet and counter space. Three cozy bedrooms with plenty of closet space to accommodate your lifestyle needs. Well-maintained front yard with lush greenery, creating a welcoming curb appeal. Expansive backyard, ideal for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the fresh air. Private driveway and detached garage offering convenient parking and extra storage space. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own this lovely, adorable home!
